# {{computing}} One of a number of [[array]]-like [[data structure|data structures]] where the [[index|indices]] are not limited to [[integers]].  A collection of memory elements in which each element is referenced by the name of the '''associative array''' together with a combination of one or more [[key|keys]], one key for each "dimension" of the array.

